There are statues of Sir [[Alf Ramsey]] and Sir [[Bobby Robson]], both former [[Ipswich Town F.C.|Ipswich Town]] and [[England national football team|England]] managers, outside the ground.<ref>{{cite news
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/2130373.stm
