==Other uses==

[[File:Bobby Robson Statue Closeup.jpg|thumb|right|upright|alt=Close-up of a bronze statue of Sir Bobby Robson, former Ipswich and England manager, in one of his typical poses|Statue of Sir Bobby Robson]]
On 20 August 2003, Portman Road hosted its first and thus far only senior [[England national football team|England]] fixture, a friendly against [[Croatia national football team|Croatia]],<ref>{{cite news
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/england/3000152.stm
| title = FA chooses Portman Road
