| title =  England 3 Croatia 1
| publisher =[[The Football Association]]
| accessdate =12 October 2007
}}</ref> The stadium has been used by England youth teams on a number of occasions, the first on 24 November 1971, saw the England U23 team draw 1<U+2013>1 with Switzerland.<ref>{{Cite web
| url = http://www.thefa.com/England/SeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2003/06/52849.htm
